metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  TREATAS({"Fashions Direct"}, 'Store'[Chain])

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
    __DS0FilterTable,
    "v_This_Year_Sales_Goal", IGNORE('Sales'[_This Year Sales Goal]),
    "This_Year_Sales", IGNORE('Sales'[This Year Sales]),
    "Regular_Sales_Units", IGNORE('Sales'[Regular_Sales_Units])
  )

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
  TREATAS({"Fashions Direct"}, 'Store'[Chain])

EVALUATE
  SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
    __DS0FilterTable,
    "This_Year_Sales", IGNORE('Sales'[This Year Sales]),
    "v_This_Year_Sales_Goal", IGNORE('Sales'[_This Year Sales Goal])
  )

DEFINE
  VAR __H0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Fashions Direct"}, 'Store'[Chain])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Item'[Category],
      "This_Year_Sales", 'Sales'[This Year Sales],
      "SalesThis_Year_Sales", IGNORE(CALCULATE('Sales'[This Year Sales], KEEPFILTERS(__H0FilterTable)))
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [This_Year_Sales], 0, 'Item'[Category], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [This_Year_Sales] DESC, 'Item'[Category]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZE(

  __DS0BodyLimited

metrics.visualTitle: Total Sales Variance %, Sales Per Sq Ft e This Year Sales por District e District

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Fashions Direct"}, 'Store'[Chain])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'District'[District],
      __DS0FilterTable,
      "Total_Sales_Variance__", 'Sales'[Total Sales Variance %],
      "Sales_Per_Sq_Ft", 'Sales'[Sales Per Sq Ft],
      "This_Year_Sales", 'Sales'[This Year Sales]
    )

  VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

  VAR __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample = 
    SAMPLECARTESIANPOINTSBYCOVER(3500, __DS0Core, [Total_Sales_Variance__], [Sales_Per_Sq_Ft])

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample

ORDER BY
  'District'[District]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    TREATAS({"Fashions Direct"}, 'Store'[Chain])

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Store'[Territory], __DS0FilterTable, "This_Year_Sales", 'Sales'[This Year Sales])

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(3502, __DS0Core, [This_Year_Sales], 0, 'Store'[Territory], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [This_Year_Sales] DESC, 'Store'[Territory]
